283
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,900
Real job, Tommy.

284
00:12:16,900 --> 00:12:18,400
"Real job," huh?

285
00:12:18,900 --> 00:12:19,700
Let's see.

286
00:12:20,100 --> 00:12:21,200
"Busboy.

287
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,500
"Car wash.

288
00:12:24,300 --> 00:12:25,400
Janitor?"

289
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:27,600
