tested clean for drugs.

312
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:15,900
Guy was making
a go of it.

313
00:13:15,900 --> 00:13:17,400
Got to respect
the effort.

314
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:19,400
Just found a report
on the arrest of Peter Doyle

315
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:21,200
