316
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:22,900
Weapons charge.

317
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:25,000
So much for regular life.

318
00:13:25,100 --> 00:13:27,700
Oh, not the father-
the son, Petey Jr.

319
00:13:28,300 --> 00:13:30,100
Not the choirboy
his mother said.

320
00:13:30,300 --> 00:13:33,300
Picked up at St. Alvin's Prep
with a gun,

