you might've gone after him.

351
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:44,500
Lot of anger, frustration...

352
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:46,000
Yeah, I was angry.

353
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:48,500
I was the kid
whose dad was locked away.

354
00:14:48,500 --> 00:14:50,300
That was my identity.

355
00:14:50,400 --> 00:14:52,300
Pistol Pete's son.

356
00:14:53,100 --> 00:14:54,400
I brought the gun to school,

357
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:55,700
showed everyone they were right,

358
00:14:55,700 --> 00:14:57,400
