359
00:14:58,100 --> 00:14:58,900
Not my happiest time.

360
00:14:58,900 --> 00:15:01,500
Understandable,
way he abandoned you.

361
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:05,000
I'd write him letters.

362
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:07,200
Like he cared.

363
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:11,300
I was convinced
that he would break out

364
00:15:11,900 --> 00:15:13,500
