365
00:15:17,500 --> 00:15:18,700
Ridiculous, huh?

366
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:20,000
When he finally did show up?

367
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,600
He wasn't any kind of legend.

368
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,900
Mom said you only
saw him one time.

369
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:26,900
Yeah, once he was back.

370
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:28,500
Knowing he was there,

371
