00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,400
- between you and Pete.
- Yeah.

459
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:56,500
I took it personal.

460
00:19:56,900 --> 00:19:58,300
Every score he made.

461
00:19:58,700 --> 00:20:01,900
Every time he flashed a roll
of dirty money in a bar.

462
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:03,900
That smug grin on his face.

463
00:20:04,800 --> 00:20:05,800
But I didn't want to kill him.

464
00:20:05,800 --> 00:20:07,800
- What did you want?
- Put him where he belonged.

465
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:09,000
Prison.

